USAGE
Basic Command

./fasta-basic-stats_cli.py -i path/to/input.fasta -o custum/name

Arguments:
-i / --input → required: Path to the FASTA file
-o / --output → Optional: Custom base name for the report files


This will:
Print a full report to the terminal
Save a TXT report named: custom/name.txt in the same folder as the input file

You can file an example .fna file in Example files

Notes
Reports are saved in the same directory as the input FASTA file by default
Use the -o option to customize the report name
Ensure your FASTA files are properly formatted to avoid errors
